Authentication system:
- Register: /register/ (username, email, password)
- Login: /login/ (Django built-in LoginView)
- Logout: /logout/ (Django built-in LogoutView)
- Profile: /profile/ (view/edit username, email, bio, avatar)

How to run locally:
1. python manage.py makemigrations
2. python manage.py migrate
3. python manage.py runserver

Notes:
- Forms use CSRF tokens.
- Avatars saved to MEDIA_ROOT; ensure MEDIA_URL and MEDIA_ROOT set in settings.py.
